  "prompt": "How is life in kochi?",
  "response": "Kochi (also known as Cochin) is a vibrant coastal city in Kerala, South India, known for its good quality of life. Here are some aspects of life in Kochi:\n\n1. Culture\n- Diverse and cosmopolitan\n- Rich cultural heritage\n- Mix of traditional Kerala and modern influences\n- Multiple languages spoken (Malayalam, English)\n\n2. Climate\n- Tropical climate\n- Warm and humid throughout the year\n- Monsoon season from June to September\n\n3. Economy\n- Growing IT and technology hub\n- Strong maritime and trade sector\n- Emerging startup ecosystem\n- Good job opportunities\n\n4. Infrastructure\n- Well-developed public transportation\n- Modern amenities\n- Good healthcare facilities\n- International airport\n\n5. Lifestyle\n- Relaxed and peaceful\n- Good food culture\n- Multiple entertainment options\n- Multicultural environment\n\n6. Cost of Living\n- Relatively affordable compared to other major Indian cities\n- Reasonable housing and living expenses\n\n7. Education\n- Quality educational institutions\n- Good schools and colleges\n- Growing number of professional courses\n\n8. Tourism\n- Popular tourist destination\n- Beautiful backwaters\n- Historic sites\n- Cultural attractions\n\nOverall, Kochi offers a balanced lifestyle with modern conveniences and traditional charm.",
